{"tid":2180904,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚凱邦接獲9個案涉被僱主威迫病毒檢測","createTime":"2020-08-30T08:13:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T08:16:42.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2857af2a163e82ef590b575fdf078ddeb69f2ca4","tid":2180904,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:13:53.000Z","msg":"全民自願參與的普及社區檢測計劃（全民檢測）9月1日開展，新民主同盟荃灣區議員譚凱邦今（30日）召開記者會表示，至今接獲9宗個案涉被僱主威迫進行新型冠狀病毒檢測，其中4宗和全民檢測計劃有關，包括一名公務員。他引述該名公務員表示，部門主管口頭上強烈呼籲員工積極參與及配合政府的檢測計劃。<br />\n<br />\n至於其他3宗與全民檢測相關的個案，譚凱邦稱包括一名百佳超級市場的員工，該員工稱百佳發出內部通告，強烈呼籲員工參加檢測；另一宗與茶飲店有關；餘下一宗仍在核實。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200830/s00001/1598773673351/%e8%ad%9a%e5%87%b1%e9%82%a6%e6%8e%a5%e7%8d%b29%e5%80%8b%e6%a1%88%e6%b6%89%e8%a2%ab%e5%83%b1%e4%b8%bb%e5%a8%81%e8%bf%ab%e7%97%85%e6%af%92%e6%aa%a2%e6%b8%ac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200830%2Fs00001%2F1598773673351%2F%25e8%25ad%259a%25e5%2587%25b1%25e9%2582%25a6%25e6%258e%25a5%25e7%258d%25b29%25e5%2580%258b%25e6%25a1%2588%25e6%25b6%2589%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e5%2583%25b1%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%25bf%25ab%25e7%2597%2585%25e6%25af%2592%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%25b8%25ac&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLFKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=9162d403\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200830%2Fs00001%2F1598773673351%2F%25e8%25ad%259a%25e5%2587%25b1%25e9%2582%25a6%25e6%258e%25a5%25e7%258d%25b29%25e5%2580%258b%25e6%25a1%2588%25e6%25b6%2589%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e5%2583%25b1%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%25bf%25ab%25e7%2597%2585%25e6%25af%2592%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%25b8%25ac&h=1d42caf9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200830/s00001/1598773673351/%e8%ad%9a%e5%87%b1%e9%82%a6%e6%8e%a5%e7%8d%b29%e5%80%8b%e6%a1%88%e6%b6%89%e8%a2%ab%e5%83%b1%e4%b